# Movie Review Sentiment Analysis using LSTM (PyTorch)

This repository contains a **complete deep learning project** for text sentiment classification using **LSTM (Long Short-Term Memory)** with PyTorch.  
The model is trained to classify movie reviews into **Positive** or **Negative** sentiment.

